Advance Auto carries (carried) alot of TRW stuff - mostly engine stuff and 
a few suspension parts.

TRW is a OEM supplier for several car manufacturers for different things. 
Locally they have a factory that assembles airbags for about 8 or 9 car 
manufacturers.


